# Section 1: Basic Content
## Demonstrating automatic numbering

This section shows what slides look like with a basic footer configuration that only includes page numbers.

---
layout: content
---

# Normal Content Slide

This slide shows the basic configuration:
- Header: **Disabled**
- Footer: **Page numbers only**
- Position: **Right**
- Format: **"2 / 8"**

Numbering started on slide 2 (excluding the cover) and will appear on all slides except the closing one.

